reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Super stylish & comfy
reviews.reviewText: Great quality. Easy assembly. Super cute boho look.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars STURDY, LEVEL, SAFE & GORGEOUS!
reviews.reviewText: I ordered 4 stools. They arrived in 3 days! They were carefully packaged and easy to assemble (one person can do it). The base is sturdy, floor protectors are already installed and level. Excellent quality seat. Cane is beautiful with slight variations of color which make them look expensive against the solid wood back. Height is as described. When the stools are pushed all the way forward, the fabric seat touches the island instead of the legs, so it will never scratch! I figured I'd only need 3 stools based on counter length calculations, but the package of 4 wasn't much more. Once assembled, I actually like having 4 since the stools are narrow! Another bonus: my dog is blind, so the simple c-shape base prevents injury. We love them!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Cute and not bulky but only ‘acceptable’ quality.
reviews.reviewText: I like these barstools a lot and I will be keeping them because they are perfect for small spaces. They have clean simple lines that keep a space from feeling cluttered. They are super cute and the rattan is real, not plastic imitation. The seat isn’t very plush, but it doesn’t hurt either- which is hard to come by when you have chronic back pain. I give four stars because although I feel that the quality is passable on these chairs, the cantilever nature of them have a natural sort of ‘give’. So they kind of rock a little bit like an ikea poang if you’ve ever sat in one of those. I personally like it now that I’m used to it and confident I’m not going to fall or break the chair. But I was admittedly hoping for sturdier construction. And despite all my measurements they are still slightly smaller than expected. All that being said, they are cute, functional, comfortable, and lightweight. I’m happy with my purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to assemble
reviews.reviewText: Beautiful barstools! Comes with all supplies needed to assemble and took less than 15 minutes. These are the shorter chairs and fit well under a normal size counter height bar. Could probably have done the higher ones for more of a “barstool” look but I am happy with my purchase!

reviews.reviewText: The stools came together with my space better than imagined. I was worried about the material of the seating but to my surprise was perfect. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 1, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Really like the counter high chairs. They are comfortable and solid. I ordered 4 and 3 were damaged. I returned all 4 for a refund. I returned the chairs in the original box to show how damaged the box was. The box the chairs were shipped in appeared too small and the packaging around the base legs of the chairs didn't have adequate protection for the legs. They had deep scratches, some down to bare metal. Because I like the product I ordered two more and hopefully I get the my refund and 2 more chairs undamaged. Otherwise I would have rated this product a 4.
